      "span_text": "Moreover, transgenic overexpression of axin, a negative regulator of wnt signaling, which promotes ␤-catenin degradation, resulted in widespread thymocyte apoptosis.  Thus, the available evidence suggests that active, signaling-competent ␤-catenin is dependent on wnt signals and independent of the pre-TCR."
